&lt;a href="http://alimsvi.ir/blog/posts/ehtemal-dar-python-1.html#rest_code_261770fb226041bb9a2112f7a56c3712-9"&gt; 9&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="http://alimsvi.ir/blog/posts/ehtemal-dar-python-1.html#rest_code_261770fb226041bb9a2112f7a56c3712-10"&gt;10&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="http://alimsvi.ir/blog/posts/ehtemal-dar-python-1.html#rest_code_261770fb226041bb9a2112f7a56c3712-11"&gt;11&lt;/a&gt;
